text: i will write no significant words here as you know akele me hi apni feelings batata hun apne bhai ko me but love you bhai jarur kahunga , aur han mere bhi anshu aye the tum sabse pehle jab me pehle se hi nostalgic bad trip leta tha. only difference is you guys realized it later.

text: Bhai apna hero h. Mje dilaye tune sabse jyada ME com me. Loved your story.intiatives lete raho and life me angrej bane raho
author: Manvendra  Singh

text: Room pr jyada time pass kiya h tere , bhar jate samay to bhane teyar rakhta tha tu aur iss bar bhi ghar ka bhana dekar college nhi aya gille shikwe to rahenge but bhai h tu yad rakhio baki yamul and burla betiC nikle bhut dukh hota h. End me courses sath me krke mja aya. Love you bhai
author: Manvendra  Singh

text: mere lab partner bhut dukh hua second yr ke bad labs krne me aap jo nhi the sath me kaam krna pda isliye. orientation se lekar bhut pakaya me janta hun mene but you were the first person i opened up with. aur khyaal rakhna apna bhi gujrati dhokle ka bhi smaj ja ab.
author: Manvendra  Singh

text: Shuru se end tak sare labs sath me ki aur kam krke mja aya, bhai in future startup me kaam ho to jarur btana. Dusro ko gali dene me apni meri tarf se deep understanding thi ğŸ˜‰. Likhte acha ho and sunate raho bhai ko
author: Manvendra  Singh

text: you judged me when we first met every one does. but bata bhi deta h tu then i know mere bare me sab acha tha so i was happy haha, bhai course madad nhi ki tune aur batra ne to drop krna pda but  thanks to  bath for taking midsem with me XD. aur football me apan logo se acha defender nhi hoga kisi team meas  we were damn serious about the job (including deb). khayal rakhna aur ese hi sabko motivate krte rehna mushkil waqt me . love from a wingmate;
author: Manvendra  Singh

text: You were unpredictable guy, pta nhi shyd hi koi course kiya ho sath me but hall me backchodi bhut kati h , last me unexpectedly mota bhi ho gya tu gym join krle ya fir football khelte rehna, love from dtop familyâ¤ï¸
author: Manvendra  Singh

text: mere dusra roomie bhut pyar tha tujhpr ,sage bhai jese rakha, khabi nhi socha tujhse khuch bolne se pehle aur dusro ke samne ladai aur discussion me kabhi kabhi agree krna dono kiya h tere sath. aur vo jo banda aaa rha tha tujhe second yr me pitne tension nhi lene ka tera bhai h ga*d tod deta uski me. yaad krne betho to bhut kisse h , bas tu apna khyal rakhna aur gali kam diya kr mujhe . simping daru aur jhagde kam krna age ,love you bro .
author: Manvendra  Singh

text:
Rommie itni harkaton ke bad bhi jinda bach gya mere hatho se sukar h rab ka. First year me to kush tha bad me thoda dukhi dukhi rha. Pta nhi meri vjh se ya bandi ka chakkr tha. Koi ni bhai h tere sath mje lene ke liye ğŸ˜‰.
Ghar pr milte h ğŸ˜‚ aunty ko bhi bol dena karuna kaal ke bad aunga

text: mech tere liye easy thi hamare liye nhi, bas jaldi beet gye vo khushi ke pal movies ,night parties ,vo saste nashe vala dance aur tera ekdam se chillana, VG ka password change kr deta tha bhadwa lekin end me router lag hi gye. will miss our gang aur chingali ki lena sath me. aur fir abhi ye sab khtm ho jaye ghumne chalenge sath me.love you bhai
